            <blockquote class="answer">
                <p>
                    DOE CODE does not directly disseminate software projects. Access to the software/code is provided by the originating site. 
                    From the DOE CODE software record page, OSTI provides a link directly to a landing page or repository depending on the project type, 
                    or provides the contact email for users to reach out to the developer or developing organization to request access to the software.
                </p>
